Rated: Guidance Suggested. This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: tabata workout
des:
Tabata Workout for Alexa guides you through the Tabata routine; A 20 second burst of high-intensity exercise followed by a 10 second recovery period.

Any exercise can be used; be that bodyweight exercises (sit-ups, push-ups, squats, lunges, etc.), kettlebells, dumbbells or interval running. 

The goal is to complete the most amount of repetitions within the time whilst practicing good form. 

The default workout repeats for 8 sets lasting 4 minutes. 
The workout can also be customised by asking Alexa to start a workout for x number of sets.

Examples:
“Alexa, open Tabata Workout” – Opens the skill main menu.
“Alexa, ask Tabata Workout to start” – Starts a default workout of 8 sets.
“Alexa, ask Tabata Workout to start a 10 set workout” – Starts a custom workout of 10 sets.
